---
title: Tex-Mex Beef Rump & Roast Veggie Salad with Sweetcorn & Garlic Yoghurt
description: Try a taste of Mexico with a difference! We're giving golden veggies and mixed leaves a flavour boost with tender beef rump rubbed with mild Tex-Mex spices. Add a dollop of garlic-infused yoghurt and crunchy charred sweetcorn for a feast worthy of a fiesta!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving*
